t;eliminate the hole&quot;."},{"pid":"d3e529a41c8b85cf116f9351003d4f45fce09e64","tid":1797641,"uid":283587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T18:31:58.000Z","msg":"Topology"}]}